The [[Image:Sketcher_JoinCurves.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_JoinCurves|Sketcher JoinCurves]] tool creates a B-spline by joining two existing [[B-Splines|B-splines]] or other edges.

==Usage== <!--T:5-->

<!--T:6-->
